parameters: So, the question is how to get down there.
I took a glance around. But I couldn't spot anything that looked
like a ladder that could take us down to the plant.
Which means our remaining option is...
Yo, what about that water pipe? It can get us to the rooftop.
The water pipe, which seems to be getting its water supply from
the stream above, stretches across to the plant's roof. From
there, it continues into the building.
Looks like that's our only option. We should be able to pry
that hatch open to get inside.
